references:
  - type: dataset
    title: "EA 4FM Codebook for LLM-Assisted Qualitative Analysis"
    authors:
      - family-names: "Nelson-Zutter"
        given-names: "Graham"
        orcid: "https://orcid.org/0009-0003-9567-6512"
    year: 2026
    doi: "10.5281/zenodo.20483207"
    repository-code: "https://github.com/aestra-research/4fm-codebook"
    notes: >-
      Methodological predecessor to this 12FEP codebook. Built first (Oct 25–29,
      2025) using a per-LLM iteration + single-LLM self-merge + multi-LLM
      cross-merge + researcher selection protocol against four primary Längle
      sources (1992, 2002, 2003, 2011). This 12FEP codebook refines and
      simplifies that protocol (parallel start + cross-LLM merges + LLM jury
      vote, two primary Längle sources only) and decomposes the four
      Fundamental Motivations into 12 Existential Prerequisites.
